title: 'Looks good
body: '3.0 out of 5 stars''Have used Nayasa buckets in past but now the quality has degraded a lot. The buckets are very thin and if you press from sides  they just go in and out. I doubt if they are durable in longer run. Buckets in local market are thicker than this and half the cost. Talking abt the look it looks beautiful. The square shape adds more appeal to its appearance. Was nicely packed  and was delivered without a single scratch.'
